                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Policeman</hi>, 89 <hi rend="italic">R</hi>). The prisoner was given into my custody—I told him what he was charged with—he said, "All right, I'll go with you"—these clothes were lying at his feet; he had just taken them of—he had his own clothes on under them.</p>
